[h1]Declaring a Class[/h1]

Begin your class definition with the keyword [b]class[/b]. Follow the keyword with the class name and the class body, enclosed in a set of curly braces. 
The following code declares a class called [b]BankAccount[/b]: [code format="cpp"][b]class [/b]BankAccount {

};[/code]
[note]A class definition must be followed by a [b]semicolon[/b].[/note]

quizzes.question:
